"        <b>CEF (gstcefsrc)</b>: Experimental Chromium-based backend using "
"GStreamer.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        <b>WPE WebKit</b>: Backend bawaan untuk wallpaper web.\n"
"        <b>CEF (gstcefsrc)</b>: Backend eksperimental berbasis Chromium yang menggunakan GStreamer.\n"
"        "

